<h3>Request from Bank</h3>
You can only request upto a total loan amount from the bank of 25,000$ or 10% of your sales turnover.<br>
<form id="loan_from_bank_form" class="form-inline" method="post" action="/investors_submit_bank" accept-charset="utf-8">
  <div class="form-group">
    <div class="input-group">
      <div class="input-group-addon">$</div>
      <input id="amount_input_loan_from_bank_form" type="number" min="1" class="form-control" name="amount" placeholder="Amount" required>
    </div>
  </div>
  <br><br>
  <div class="form-group">
    <div class="input-group">
      <div class="input-group-addon"><i class="fa fa-calendar"></i></div>
      <input type="number" min="1" max="90" class="form-control" name="repay_time" placeholder="Loan Period" required>
    </div>
  </div>
  (in Days)<br>
    +0.2% Interst Rate per Additional Day
  <br><br>
  Request loan for:
    <select name="company_id" class="form-control" required>
      <%Company.where(:user_id => current_user.id).each do |company|%>
        <option value="<%=company.id%>"><%=company.name%></option>
      <%end%>
    </select>
  <br><br>
  <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">Request Loan for Bank</button>
</form>
  
